"title": "5344: imprisonment",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5344",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Being confined in prison is used both literally and figuratively in Scripture. Release from prison is used as a picture of freedom from spiritual bondage.</p>\n<h2>The anticipation or threat of imprisonment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:25-Matt5:26\">MAT 5:25–5:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:58\">LUK 12:58</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:23\">ACT 20:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Imprisonment for law-breaking</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:26\">EZR 7:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:3\">GEN 40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:4\">2KI 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:11\">JER 52:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:30\">MAT 18:30</a></p>\n<h2>Imprisonment while on remand</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:33-Num15:34\">NUM 15:33–15:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:12\">LEV 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:16\">MAT 27:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:7\">MRK 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:19\">LUK 23:19</a></p>\n<h2>Imprisonment of the innocent, often with malicious intent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:28\">JER 38:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12\">LUK 21:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:20-Gen39:22\">GEN 39:20–39:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:14-Gen40:15\">GEN 40:14–40:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:16-Gen42:17\">GEN 42:16–42:17</a> <em>Joseph planning the welfare of his brothers</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:27\">1KI 22:27</a> <em>Ahab orders Micaiah's imprisonment</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:10\">2CH 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:2-Jer32:3\">JER 32:2–32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:3\">MAT 14:3</a> <em>John the Baptist imprisoned by Herod</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:3\">ACT 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:23-Acts16:24\">ACT 16:23–16:24</a> <em>Paul and Silas in prison</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:19\">ACT 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:29\">ACT 23:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:27\">ACT 24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:10\">ACT 26:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:31\">ACT 26:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23\">2CO 11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:36\">HEB 11:36</a></p>\n<h2>Release from imprisonment</h2>\n<h3>By earthly rulers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:14\">GEN 41:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:27\">2KI 25:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:31\">JER 52:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:13-Jer39:14\">JER 39:13–39:14</a></p>\n<h3>By divine intervention</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:7\">PSA 146:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:6\">PSA 68:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:20\">PSA 102:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:10-Ps107:14\">PSA 107:10–107:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:7\">PSA 142:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:7\">ISA 42:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:9\">ISA 49:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:14\">ISA 51:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:1-Acts12:11\">ACT 12:1–12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Imprisonment used in a figurative or poetic sense</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:10\">JOB 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:14\">JOB 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:11\">PSA 66:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:14\">ECC 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:23\">ROM 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:22-Gal3:23\">GAL 3:22–3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:19\">1PE 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7\">REV 20:7</a></p>",
